Paper: hep-th/9405173

Date: 1994-05-26

Title: Generalized Gaussian Effective Potential

Authors: P.Cea and L.Tedesco

Comments: tex, 10 pages + 4 Postscript figures included

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B335 (1994) 423-427

We study a generalization of the Gaussian effective potential forself-interacting scalar fields in one and two spatial dimensions. We computethe two-loop corrections and discuss the renormalization of the generalizedGaussian effective potential.